[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0908","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0908.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0834","title":"RSA Security RSAREF 2.0 加密解密函数缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"RSAREF 2.0 是 RSA Security 发布的加密参考实现库，其加密和解密函数中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向受影响函数传递特制输入数据触发栈溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。由于该库被广泛集成到各类安全应用中，漏洞影响范围较大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0834"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-01","updated":"1999-12-01","remediation":"RSAREF 2.0 已停止维护，建议用户迁移至更现代的加密库如 OpenSSL 或 Bouncy Castle，避免使用存在已知缓冲区溢出漏洞的旧版本 RSAREF 库。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/843"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0908.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0659","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0659.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0860","title":"Sun Solaris chkperm 符号链接攻击致敏感文件泄露漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中的 chkperm 工具存在安全漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置 VMSYS 环境变量并结合符号链接攻击，以 bin 用户权限读取系统上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击条件为拥有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0860"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-12-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级到不受影响的 Solaris 版本或安装 Sun 官方提供的安全补丁。如无法升级，应限制不可信用户对系统的本地访问权限，并监控 chkperm 工具的异常使用行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T08:46:31.379853350+00:00","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/837"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0659.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0659.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0659.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0631","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0631.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0841","title":"Sun Solaris CDE dtmail 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统中 CDE（Common Desktop Environment）的 dtmail 邮件工具存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。当用户打开或处理特制邮件时，程序未能正确校验输入长度，导致攻击者可通过构造超长邮件内容覆盖栈上返回地址并执行任意代码。攻击条件为本地用户能够诱导目标用户使用 dtmail 打开恶意邮件，成功利用后可获取目标用户权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0841"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-01","updated":"1999-12-01","remediation":"升级到 Sun 发布的 Solaris 补丁集群（如 Solaris 2.6 的 105632 系列补丁），或禁用 CDE dtmail 改用其他邮件客户端，并限制本地用户对邮件工具的执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"1999-12-01T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0841","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/832"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0631.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0900","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0900.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0822","title":"Qualcomm qpopper 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Qualcomm Qpopper 3.0/3.0 b20 POP3 服务器的 AUTH 命令处理存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可发送超长的特制 AUTH 命令参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址实现任意代码执行并获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Qpopper 3.0 及 3.0 b20 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0 严重级别，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，ExploitDB 已公开利用代码。受影响系统需升级至修复版本或禁用易受攻击的 POP3 服务。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0822"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.833","remediation":"建议立即升级 Qualcomm qpopper 到 3.0.1 版本或更高版本（如 4.0 版本），该版本已修复 AUTH 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞。若无法立即升级，可暂时禁用 POP3 服务或在防火墙层面限制 110 端口仅允许受信任 IP 访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/830","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19646","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe9e77bf3808998cc7ef33bc8a5ea311f35fadb0/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0822.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0822","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0822.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0822.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q66x-x6v7-27j2/GHSA-q66x-x6v7-27j2.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0822.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/pop3_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/830/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0900.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0596","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0596.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0824","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Subst.exe 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT SUBST 命令存在漏洞，用户可使用 SUBST 命令将驱动器号映射到文件夹，且该映射在用户注销后不会自动取消，导致后续登录的用户访问该驱动器号时实际访问的是攻击者指定的文件夹。攻击者可利用此漏洞重定向系统文件夹或用户文件夹，导致权限提升或数据篡改。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统，攻击者需拥有本地登录权限且能执行 SUBST 命令，攻击需在攻击者注销后、受害者登录前完成映射配置。CVSS 评分 4.6，属中等危害等级。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0824"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.080","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows NT 4.0 SP6 或更高版本（如 Windows 2000），微软已在 SP6 中修复 SUBST 映射残留漏洞。若无法升级，可通过组策略禁用 SUBST 命令（用户配置→管理模板→Windows 组件→命令提示符→禁用命令提示符），或在用户注销脚本中添加 `subst * /d` 命令强制清除所有驱动器映射作为临时缓解措施。建议通过组策略限制普通用户执行 SUBST 命令权限。建议立即安装微软官方安全补丁（KB239643），或升级至 Windows 2000 SP4 以上版本彻底修复该漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/833","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d08a5c34806fec51f3d6c8b496ad617d8294f215/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0824.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0824","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0824.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0824.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jfmq-vm3j-98jr/GHSA-jfmq-vm3j-98jr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0824.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e2d59cef-34e6-4319-b1ae-0d96d601bd59.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0596.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0627","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0627.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0840","title":"Sun Solaris CDE dtmail 与 dtmailpr 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Microsystems Solaris 7 及 8 操作系统中的 CDE（通用桌面环境）dtmail 和 dtmailpr 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当本地用户通过 -f 选项向这两个程序传入超长参数时，会触发栈缓冲区溢出，攻击者可利用此漏洞以 root 权限执行任意代码，完全控制系统。该漏洞无需网络访问，本地低权限用户即可发起攻击，对系统机密性、完整性和可用性造成严重影响。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0840"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-11-30","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"应用 Oracle 或 Sun Microsystems 发布的安全补丁修复此漏洞。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份执行 chmod 755 /usr/dt/bin/dtmail /usr/dt/bin/dtmailpr 移除 setuid root 权限，阻止本地用户通过 -f 选项触发缓冲区溢出提权；或直接执行 chmod 0 禁用这两个二进制文件，改用其他邮件客户端。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securiteam.com/exploits/3J5QQPPQ0O.html","http://www.security-express.com/archives/bugtraq/1999-q4/0122.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/832","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3579","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3580","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0840.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/35cd604fbbf2927fb6acbcd700e81d36cd6dec11/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0840.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0840","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/12e9f9121122940a38e93216069cda4e01d5b051/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0840.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0840.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-32fr-c24m-729q/GHSA-32fr-c24m-729q.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/832/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0840.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0627.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0646","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0646.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0847","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9102,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10787}}","description":"free internet chess server (FICS) 程序和 xboard 终端中的 fics_program 模块存在严重缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可以通过向目标系统发送特制的国际象棋走法或终端命令，利用程序对输入缓冲区管理不善漏洞，在未经授权的情况下在远程服务器上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响广泛使用的开源国际象棋程序，攻击者无需身份验证即可远程触发，在 FICS/xboard 等版本上均可造成系统完全控制。攻击者需精心构造恶意输入数据包，诱使程序发生缓冲区边界写入，从而获取对目标主机的控制权，将系统权限提升至攻击者所用账户权限，进而进一步横向渗透或建立持久后门通道。此类缺陷典型存在于经典的国际象棋引擎程序中，源于对玩家输入校验不足和内存分配错误处理，该漏洞已在 2024 年 8 月相关安全补丁更新中修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0847"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:10.930","remediation":"tags.<value>升级到 1.7.x 或更高版本的 FICS 程序，并应用原始报告者提供的补丁。或者，考虑到 FICS 项目已在 1996 年结束开发，建议改用受支持的国际象棋服务器软件，如 Stockfish 或 Fruit，并确保完全安装最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94407791819019&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0847.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0847","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0847.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0847.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r84f-m96c-7ghv/GHSA-r84f-m96c-7ghv.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0847.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83028/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--85dbc306-9d23-45be-a4a1-57df56838caa.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/70290debf97c1057397e6f7c8c733dec0658bf76/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0646.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0633","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0633.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0842","title":"Symantec Mail-Gear 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Symantec Mail-Gear 1.0 Web界面服务器存在目录遍历漏洞，该漏洞允许未经身份验证的远程攻击者通过在文件路径参数中发送路径遍历序列（如..）来读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响Symantec Mail-Gear 1.0版本，在默认配置下，攻击者无需任何权限即可发起攻击。攻击者通过构造恶意请求访问系统敏感文件，如配置文件、密码文件、数据库文件等，导致敏感信息泄露，进而可能为进一步攻击提供信息支撑。该类型的漏洞普遍存在于未正确处理用户输入的文件访问功能中，攻击者可以利用路径遍历突破访问控制机制，读取本来无法访问的文件，严重威胁系统信息安全。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0842"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:10.313","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Symantec Mail-Gear 的后续修复版本或替换为主流邮件安全网关产品；如暂无法升级，应在前置防火墙或反向代理上拦截包含 `../`、`..%2f`、`%2e%2e` 等目录遍历序列的 HTTP 请求，并限制该 Web 管理界面仅允许受信任内网 IP 访问，同时以非特权低权限系统账户运行该服务以缩小任意文件读取的影响范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1144","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/827","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=NCBBKFKDOLAGKIAPMILPCEAFCBAA.labs%40ussrback.com","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19644","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/082f2f7e857643469b13565b89f2acba96998d2e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0842.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0842","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0842.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/44e56ab96b4cc04024678e20a1f15145c3b3cc59/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0842.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pj29-f7xw-w37p/GHSA-pj29-f7xw-w37p.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0842.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d36357d8-ad61-426b-ac27-a8ad141270c3.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000899.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/db2259ea67d1f5e8ce454c4a2cee60d344017bd3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0633.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0625","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0625.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0839","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Internet Explorer 计划任务权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统在安装 Internet Explorer 5 后，其任务计划程序（Task Scheduler）存在权限提升漏洞。已通过身份认证的用户可在任务被计划调度之后，通过修改该任务的配置内容（如执行命令或参数）来提升自身权限，从而以更高权限（如系统级权限）执行任意操作。该漏洞影响安装 IE 5 的 Windows NT 系统，攻击前提是攻击者需拥有本地普通用户账户并能访问任务计划程序所创建的任务文件。利用方式较为简单，攻击者只需在任务调度后篡改任务定义即可实现本地权限提升，CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0839"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.937","remediation":"建议升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 版本以修复该漏洞，或通过控制面板卸载 IE 5 离线浏览包以消除任务计划程序组件。如无法立即升级，可临时禁用 IE 5 Offline Browsing Pack 中的任务计划程序功能，或阻止普通用户对 C:\\WINNT\\Tasks 目录的写入权限作为缓解措施，并尽快应用 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-051 对应的补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ246972","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/828","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-051","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/082f2f7e857643469b13565b89f2acba96998d2e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0839.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0839","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0839.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/44e56ab96b4cc04024678e20a1f15145c3b3cc59/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0839.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-26g5-98pg-gvr8/GHSA-26g5-98pg-gvr8.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0839.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--65a10b93-8a1e-4d1c-8239-355070a53288.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0625.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0041","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0041.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0387","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 遗留凭据缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows 95和Windows 98系统中存在一个从Windows for Workgroups继承的遗留凭据缓存机制，该机制会在RAM中以明文形式缓存网络登录凭据。虽然该机制在Windows 95/98中已不再使用，但代码仍被保留。攻击者若拥有物理访问权限且系统自上次网络会话后未重启，可通过查询该缓存获取上一个网络用户的明文密码，导致敏感凭据泄露。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0387"],"sources":["cve","ms"],"published":"1999-11-29","updated":"1999-11-29","remediation":"微软已发布安全公告MS99-052修复此漏洞。Windows 95用户应安装KB168115更新补丁，Windows 98用户应安装对应安全更新。Windows 98第二版不受此漏洞影响。建议用户及时安装补丁并限制物理访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:25:41.557377081+00:00","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ168115","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/829","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-052"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0041.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0643","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0643.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0845","title":"SCO UnixWare su 程序缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SCO UnixWare su(1) 程序存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞，因未对用户名参数长度进行边界检查，本地攻击者可通过向 su 命令传递超长用户名参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址实现任意代码执行，从而将权限从普通用户提升至 root。该漏洞影响 SCO UnixWare 2.1、7.0、7.0.1、7.1、7.1.1 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2（高危），攻击向量为本地，需攻击者具备合法本地账户并能执行 su 命令，利用方式为构造超长用户名参数触发栈溢出劫持控制流获取 root shell。SCO 已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议升级至修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0845"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:10.687","remediation":"立即将系统升级到最新的Red Hat Enterprise Linux或Ubuntu LTS发行版，或应用最新的SCO Unixware安全补丁；如无法立即升级，可通过修改su程序验证逻辑长度限制和加强用户权限控制来临时缓解漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0845","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19643","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/49836c1c79a31c6cbe258de560530ef5be1db5f4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0845.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0845","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0845.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0845.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-94j9-vgcm-q47x/GHSA-94j9-vgcm-q47x.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0845.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3f06bc7c-a156-4766-a566-56d90e5f5258.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0643.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0023","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0023.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0317","title":"Linux su 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux su 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 su 程序传递特制的长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而将普通用户权限提升至 root 超级管理员权限。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 内核版本中的 su 组件，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，一旦成功可完全控制目标系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0317"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-11-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.383","remediation":"立即升级 shadow-utils（shadow）软件包至最新版本，所有现代 Linux 发行版均已修复此漏洞。Red Hat 系执行 `yum update shadow-utils`，Debian 系执行 `apt-get update && apt-get install --only-upgrade shadow`。如无法升级，限制非授权用户的本地 shell 访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0317"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0023.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1176","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1176.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1548","title":"Cabletron SmartSwitch Router 8000 ARP Flooding 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cabletron SmartSwitch Router (SSR) 8000 路由器在固件版本 2.x 中存在 ARP 请求处理能力的设计缺陷，其每秒仅能处理约 200 个 ARP 请求。位于同一广播域或二层网络中的攻击者，可向目标设备发送超过该速率限制的 ARP 请求洪水（ARP flooding），耗尽设备的处理能力，导致合法 ARP 请求无法被正常响应，进而引发网络中断或服务不可用的拒绝服务（DoS）攻击。该漏洞影响运行 2.x 固件版本的 SSR 8000 系列设备，攻击者无需身份认证，仅需具备向目标网络发送大量 ARP 包的能力即可利用，CVSS 评分约为 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1548"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:41.563","remediation":"建议将 Cabletron SmartSwitch Router 8000 固件升级至 3.0 或更高版本，该版本提升了 ARP 请求处理能力并修复了 ARP 泛洪拒绝服务问题。如暂无法升级，可在路由器上配置 ARP 速率限制或入口过滤（如启用端口安全、限制每端口学习速率），并在上游边界防火墙/ACL 上对 ARP 广播流量进行限速，以缓解大规模 ARP 请求泛洪攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://razor.bindview.com/publish/advisories/adv_Cabletron.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/821","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1548.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1548","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1548.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2a20296d4b03dbd5c5991115b8296a9f2b947592/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1548.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gv2c-5jh2-xgwq/GHSA-gv2c-5jh2-xgwq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/821/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1548.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/6136e78f1cdecae569f65737134a995b9b0383b7/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1176.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0989","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0989.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1163","title":"HP系列800 S/X/V类服务器SSP远程访问漏洞","description":"HP Series 800 S/X/V 类服务器的 Service Support Processor (SSP) Teststation 存在未授权访问漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 SSP 测试站直接获取服务器控制台访问权限，从而完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 HP 800 S/S/X/V 系列服务器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商已发布修复建议，建议用户禁用 SSP Teststation 或升级固件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1163"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.297","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9911-105 中提供的补丁 PF_CSXV1007（可从 HP Electronic Support Center FTP 获取），将 SSP/Teststation 升级至 5.1.2 版本（V22x0 产品）或 1.1.2 版本（V2500 产品）。如无法立即打补丁，应在防火墙上限制对 SSP Teststation 端口的远程访问，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94347039929958&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7439.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1163.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1163","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1163.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1163.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5vwm-x8q6-45qr/GHSA-5vwm-x8q6-45qr.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87954/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1163.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000893.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0989.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0638","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0638.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0844","title":"Deerfield MDaemon 2.8.5/2.8.6 URL 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Deerfield MDaemon 2.8.5/2.8.6 版本的 WorldClient 和 WebConfig 服务在处理过长 URL 请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可通过发送超长的 URL 请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃并造成拒绝服务攻击。该漏洞影响 MDaemon 2.8.5/2.8.6 及 Alt-N WorldClient Pro 2.0.0.0/2.0.1.0/Standard 2.0.0.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程发送超长 URL 触发漏洞，导致邮件服务中断，CVSS 评分 5.0 属中等严重度。厂商已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议升级至修复版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0844"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:10.560","remediation":"升级 Deerfield MDaemon 至 2.8.7 或更高版本，该版本已修复 WorldClient 与 WebConfig 服务因超长 URL 导致的拒绝服务问题；如暂无法升级，可在 Web 服务器前端（如反向代理）配置 URL 长度限制（建议不超过 2048 字节）并限制异常高频请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/820","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/823","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19640","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/49836c